enentech, South San Francisco, CA.', 'Futibatinib, Entrectinib, Regorafenib, Copanlisib, Trametinib, Erlotinib, Ponatinib, Neratinib, Erdafitinib, Nintedanib, Capmatinib, More', 'Idelalisib, Tivozanib', 1767369485);
